Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.47,0:01:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for treating us today, Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That was good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel happy when the egg tastes good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The price of gas went up two yen since yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.61,0:01:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Should've filled up the tank...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:48.67,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Why is it that people who spend generously...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:51.29,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,...care so much about a one yen difference in the price of gasoline?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That book I lent you a while ago is apparently getting turned into a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be buying it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so behind, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I reserved the limited edition as soon as it was announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.49,0:02:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I even bought the DVD box set for the anime and other related goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more hooked than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty common for people to become bigger fans than the people who recommend stuff to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how Yui-neesan chose her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to someone else's influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Her car!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I lent her a racing manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That sure surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary how much energy people put into their hobbies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday was the third win in a row, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the start of a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If they keep on winning,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the playoffs and Japan Series aren't out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:33.37,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:35.63,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Probably pro baseball, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All the way to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.27,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Sensei enjoys it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, baseball's all about...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:38.84,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Speaking of baseball...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The famous poet, Masaoka Shiki, apparently loved baseball a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He played catcher until he was too ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And he took his childhood name, Noboru,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,wrote it using the characters for baseball,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and pronounced it Noball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The winners of the Major League are called the world champions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking about the Japan Series reminded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when it only includes American teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they should beat our teams before they call themselves world champions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's awfully pumped up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach me how to do these!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unusual for you to be asking a question about schoolwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of these problems are quite difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause they're from an arcade quiz game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good with academic stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And put more effort into your studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're applying for college.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be like this here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but they call me a sage over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, just enroll in that whatever academy of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I didn't get enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How long were you up playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you're always in bed by eleven, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was thinking when I looked at Miyuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But you haven't grown much considering how much you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Onee-chan said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sensitive about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for calling so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kobayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the Iwasaki residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,May I speak with Minami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She already went to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she always sleep this early?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're having fun singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we'll make do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let my father know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,After the ground-breaking ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, there you go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm underage, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't see you gesturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a force of habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm on the phone, I have to concentrate, so I stop gaming,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but then my empty hand starts feeling lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was using a roller to get rid of dust the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Roll! Roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff like that can get pretty addictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Like random doodling or menial chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get off the phone, that stuff gets old really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:06:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda depressing when only the area around you is clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You could just finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My passion fades with the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just leave it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's kinda stinky, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's okay every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,**cky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Po***!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to do that back in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of things we did when we were little,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to stir my yogurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and go, "Bread factory!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bread factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bread factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be embarrassed. Just 'fess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,About that game I lent you back during first semester...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else wants to play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it for the squirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lent a bunch to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I should get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sure are amazing, Hiiragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day, I found these games and didn't remember who I borrowed them from...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are some I lent to other people that I've forgotten about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're way too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be a Law of Equal Lending.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a universal principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Misao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what's u{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Potemkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something super important...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget it if it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking at the numbers for the Autumn Jumbo Lottery,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but mine were all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's not so easy to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent in a bunch of postcards,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't win any prizes from the drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When you never win,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you start to wonder if the vendors or editors are running some kind of scam, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be so suspicious of other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna call it a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the bathroom first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They tell me that I talk to myself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really sleepy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so why am I so awake after that weird joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't do this at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not feeling it tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I should get to bed while I'm dozing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really sleepy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so why am I so awake just 'cause it's cold under the covers? {This doesn't work out here... Maybe "...so am I wide awake just 'cause [...]". She is wondering here, after all! Also, "so awake" sounds derpy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can fall asleep quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs are really hot for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fall asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this only happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:19.54,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,It's the season for baked sweet potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:20.56,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Well, Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.11,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:22.33,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.14,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I know, so don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.15,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.40,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:27.58,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,But you'll gain weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.70,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,You still said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.61,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,But I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.57,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Once I've made eye contact with the guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.36,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,it'd be rude not to buy one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:34.83,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:36.61,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,"Will she buy one?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:38.67,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,"My feelings will be hurt if she doesn't."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:39.95,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,That look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:41.68,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.36,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,If you make eye contact at Comiket,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:45.22,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,it's really hard to put a book back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:48.53,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,You don't care when other people have no idea what you're talking about, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:49.50,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:52.41,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about when you're hanging around a circle's booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:54.75,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,When you pick up a book in front of a sales rep,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:57.73,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,you feel pretty bad if you leave without buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:10:00.28,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,But you still put it back, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:04.06,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,There's been an increase in the number of light novels being adapted to anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:04.82,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The novel I lent you has already had three anime adaptations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And there should be a new volume coming out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've watched the anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but I haven't read the novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much text makes me tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That again, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't the games you always play have a lot more text?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They should, but it's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd really help if they released them in a visual novel format.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:29.10,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.41,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,When are they doing the fourth season of the anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:32.36,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.08,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:34.69,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Is that some kind of reference?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The lid always ends up crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, some people are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's clumsiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You share some cute flaws with Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are amazing, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can't open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I used my usual strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't open the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we just tear it along the notches?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,O-One sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll open it, so hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We can just tear along the notches or use scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that would hurt my pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Or make me feel like a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, is it a mosquito?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mosquito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get annoyed when you know something's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when you haven't been bitten yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you know it's there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you must take it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the instinct of a hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If a guy in the same year professed his love for Yu-chan or me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't that guy be a lolicon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in the same class year,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so technically, they wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But in this case, it feels like appearance holds more weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, if you were a 30-year-old who looked like someone in grade school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you could say the guy likes older women...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a complicated issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to come up with a strict definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're definitely my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami would have just ended it with, "Who cares!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell in love with Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and you dote on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,which means you're a lolicon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:12:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not entirely accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.97,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm not limited to little girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.28,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I also like normal girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.19,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,So you should say that I'm also a lolicon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:09.90,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Well, it basically depends on the character.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:12.13,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Either way, you fail as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how you're always so clingy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you still be like that if I were a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad I'm a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the bath should be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You go first, Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He chased her away 'cause he was looking bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,About Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She was short and your childhood friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she like a character out of a gal game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She was adorable since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand why you fell for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but why did she marry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like, "You wouldn't accept me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so I ended up as a gal game lover!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And she just said yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that coercion!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't the only reason, obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And she was really happy when you were born...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this mole make her look like you, Sou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She has your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can definitely tell she's our child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hope she doesn't grow up like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she doesn't inherit my height,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,or your personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,430)}Pretty harsh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did you suddenly mention her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you lonely without Mom around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You create as much excitement as two people would.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yu-chan's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata's grown up to be a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, she's not as normal as you wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't die before I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I have no intention of doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanata died young,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but she said she was happy and smiled at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard on those left behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but I want to be like that at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Death by moe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're definitely going to have a bizarre death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought a digital camera for work today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been back in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.68,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:01.44,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they're doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:02.11,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Just one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:02.93,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:04.59,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Geez! I'm in the middle of a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:05.37,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:06.62,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Okay! Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:08.43,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Come on, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dad, you're way too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so heartless, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking photos to commemorate this new camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you buy this for work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.69,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.71,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Sou-kun hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One more picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.45,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,That's right, you never did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:30.76,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,...pay much attention to what other people wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts, Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You really haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel more and more like Kanata when I hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just blurt out risqué statements!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see what Mom had to put up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad may be like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't turn into a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach me that one game once you clear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's surprisingly difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:10.90,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I think I made a wrong choice somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They play games together,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so it looks like they're getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.40,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I can't make it to the H-scene for the character I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you letting your daughter play!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you teaching her the wrong things, Sou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Mom choose you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're just a pervert, lolicon and old otaku. {Derp. Try "I mean, you are just a pervert, lolicon and old otaku.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,People usually don't go for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a little harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't go easy on your old man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanata had really good intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:39.92,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:41.82,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,You were always like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.45,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Always making me almost forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:49.28,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,...why I chose to spend...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I failed as a human being...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:53.16,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,...my life with this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...there was one thing I was absolutely sure about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing you were absolutely sure about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who loved Kanata most in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He accepts my good and bad parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's willing to show both...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...his good and bad parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The place I feel most at ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The place that lets me feel most at ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do one with Yu-chan later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:26.84,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,The fact that I can no longer be there hurts a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that would be more than one picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought this for your hobby, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just testing it out before I take pictures for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.87,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can live on inside them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...the way the two of them exist inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll continue to watch over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.44,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,May the ones who brought me so much joy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:53.10,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.36,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...be blessed with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:20:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'll be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a shadow back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A real ghost picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with my bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-Yu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:14.43,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Deleting it isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't we have to burn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't burn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've talked with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a different impression of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but Mina-rin still seems a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:50.08,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Those two are really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You had classroom duty today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the teacher still in the faculty office?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.22,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,This would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yutaka, your tie is crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Onee-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking at my friends weird again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's been building up. {What has been building up?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't find them anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't find their managers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, either way, they're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.50,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,It's rolling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a bad feeling about this show from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.18,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fact... {In fact? Fact is?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually refused in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But all that politics crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Grown-up issues and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.24,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it's rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's rolling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what? {Ja, nani? It seems like a question to me here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that the camera's rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Isono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Nakajima!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, it's the medley version!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:52.44,ED English,,0,0,0,,Mi-Miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:56.55,ED English,,0,0,0,,For-Forgot my something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.55,0:21:59.35,ED English,,0,0,0,,One clear, sunshiny day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:03.42,ED English,,0,0,0,,Take it! I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.95,ED English,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:05.58,ED English,,0,0,0,,Santa Mo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:08.48,ED English,,0,0,0,,Mi-Miracle Minorun-run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:09.45,ED English,,0,0,0,,For-For-For-For...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:11.08,ED English,,0,0,0,,One clear, sunshiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:16.61,ED English,,0,0,0,,Take it! I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.61,0:22:18.12,ED English,,0,0,0,,Dentistman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.12,0:22:19.71,ED English,,0,0,0,,Santa Moni...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:23.53,ED English,,0,0,0,,For-Forgot my something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:27.52,ED English,,0,0,0,,Forgot my something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:29.98,ED English,,0,0,0,,That fragment of memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:34.59,ED English,,0,0,0,,One clear, sunshiny day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.59,0:22:36.86,ED English,,0,0,0,,Take it! I'll still be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:40.25,ED English,,0,0,0,,I am Dentistman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:41.49,ED English,,0,0,0,,Santa Moni...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:43.59,ED English,,0,0,0,,I am Dentist...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:44.97,ED English,,0,0,0,,Santa Moni...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:49.86,ED English,,0,0,0,,I am Dentistman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:52.16,ED English,,0,0,0,,For-For-For-For-For-For!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:53.79,ED English,,0,0,0,,Minorun-run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:58.57,ED English,,0,0,0,,I am Dentistman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't change when I blew the whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You kept finishing Dentistman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.65,0:23:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.52,0:23:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.80,0:23:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Soujiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.74,0:23:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Sou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be heading off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.15,0:23:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to leave my body yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure I can learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou-kun, you're talking about manga or anime again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.73,0:23:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.23,0:23:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "A Fine Line."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fly with all the turbulence!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.69,0:23:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now...
